Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.36,0:00:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.80,0:00:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來接你了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以買肉包子給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.37,0:00:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼跟什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別靠那麼近 熱死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.87,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很燙呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.94,0:00:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.04,0:00:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 感冒感冒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.91,0:00:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以要買肉包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.11,0:00:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.31,0:00:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.85,0:00:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.51,0:00:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間的黃昏的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.69,0:01:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行著一段永遠的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.56,0:01:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的指尖繼續探索著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.74,0:01:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎片發出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.01,0:01:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊的抱住胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.25,0:01:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找遺失的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.16,0:01:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用雙手的掌心確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.83,0:01:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在新的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.24,0:01:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間開始流動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉包肉包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.76,0:02:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳啊 現在吃的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是會吃不下\N秋子阿姨煮的飯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.83,0:02:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…買其他的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.56,0:02:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼跟什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.23,0:02:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿妳沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.07,0:02:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 等我一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.81,0:02:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吃的東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.15,0:02:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.38,0:02:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看 可愛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.72,0:02:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.76,0:02:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「冬天的煙火」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.49,0:02:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是買更貴的東西就好了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.46,0:02:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去 不要再掉下來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.68,0:03:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 妳在做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.45,0:03:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個很難用嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.02,0:03:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 妳應該會用筷子吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道為什麼手好累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.73,0:03:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿湯匙給妳用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.47,0:03:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨\N這樣未免太寵她了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.54,0:03:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 這裡是水瀨家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.79,0:03:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 突然就倒了下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 那就拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.10,0:03:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以過去看診的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫計程車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.34,0:04:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一你去待在真琴的身邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 現在去醫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.29,0:04:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴她…不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.35,0:04:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.65,0:04:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哪裡 真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.18,0:04:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋\N病成那樣要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.72,0:04:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.25,0:05:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在這種地方做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.19,0:05:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我討厭醫生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不去看醫生的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來治得好的病也會治不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.83,0:05:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你…不要帶我去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.34,0:05:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.31,0:05:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會再做妳討厭的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.64,0:05:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.75,0:06:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要再跟\N這個女孩有任何牽扯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.39,0:06:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她將必定會帶給你\N無止境的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.80,0:06:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個陌生人說這種話\N一點根據都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.11,0:06:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你接下來將會看到真正的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.03,0:06:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狀況怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經穩定下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.83,0:06:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早飯要吃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.73,0:06:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校就不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該沒睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要太勉強比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.87,0:06:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.28,0:06:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天由我來照顧真琴好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在找妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道昨晚妳說的話的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.96,0:07:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫…天野美汐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於真琴她的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳幹嘛說那種話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.37,0:07:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你知道嗎？那個女孩的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.81,0:07:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 但那傢伙說過\N她對我有所怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N那是有什麼地方搞錯了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.12,0:07:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟那女孩子…\N曾經相會過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.66,0:07:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不記得是理所當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.26,0:07:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個時候\N她還沒有化為人的姿態…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在…說什麼啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.00,0:07:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 你們所在的\N「眺望之丘」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.04,0:07:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說從以前\N就住著不可思議的生物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.04,0:08:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經過長時間的歲月\N獲得妖力的狐狸們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.78,0:08:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被視為讓村子招致災禍的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自古以來\N便一直遭到人們的厭惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那應該是傳說吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.69,0:08:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩子不是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.93,0:08:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了帶給你災難而出現的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.47,0:08:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰會相信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟說她並不是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.84,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟說她是給人帶來災禍的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信不信是你的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.78,0:08:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 請先記得這句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.38,0:08:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們為了化為人的姿態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.82,0:08:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要兩個必要的代價
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代價？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.09,0:08:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記憶跟…性命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.80,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 妳到底是誰啊…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.64,0:09:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…做了一個夢呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.85,0:09:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在昨晚去的山丘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤零零的一個人在等著的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.29,0:09:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.02,0:09:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知為什麼很悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且對那個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感到非常非常的不可原諒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.10,0:09:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.47,0:09:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有人讓妳一個人\N孤零零的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.57,0:09:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.01,0:09:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想拜託你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唸那個給我聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛總是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.12,0:09:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我還小的時候\N撿到的那隻小狐狸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為誤入陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而受了很重的傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.46,0:10:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我照顧牠\N讓牠恢復到能跑為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果說\N現在在這裡的真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是牠所轉世的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.57,0:10:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣離譜的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.64,0:10:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是完全不會相信的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會來接妳的\N所以到那時候再見吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.58,0:10:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還要聽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.82,0:10:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是都已經流汗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.72,0:10:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？沒辦法弄開鈕扣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.08,0:10:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我只是不想相信而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.28,0:10:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩子不是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.73,0:11:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好辣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.53,0:11:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天開始\N真琴的情況一天比一天惡化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.95,0:11:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.43,0:11:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你\N只是在那一瞬間的奇跡裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.37,0:11:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.91,0:11:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那只是那個女孩\N生命回歸之時握在手上的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間耀眼的光芒而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.61,0:12:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.05,0:12:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的確一天比一天的衰弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.65,0:12:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像\N回到小孩子的時候一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.75,0:12:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了很多的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.49,0:12:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經很接近結束的那一刻了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.63,0:12:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天野 難道\N沒有幫助她的方法嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.03,0:12:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還縮短自己的壽命來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是為了什麼來見我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.97,0:12:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了找我報仇嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她那麼的憎恨我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是因為很寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.05,0:12:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人孤零零的被遺棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.45,0:12:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直想跟相澤你相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.89,0:12:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這種思念\N才使得奇跡發生的不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.42,0:12:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.73,0:12:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子們\N並不像傳說所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.90,0:12:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是被怨恨嫌惡的存在的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天野…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為她們真的是好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.70,0:12:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以別離\N才讓人如此的痛苦…悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.51,0:13:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天野 難道妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.04,0:13:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不想再讓誰體會到\N跟我一樣的悲傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 我向妳道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.89,0:13:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請盡可能的\N完成那女孩的心願吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.26,0:13:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瞭解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.97,0:13:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入二月後 下了第一次的大雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.91,0:13:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴漸漸的\N甚至連話都不會說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.41,0:13:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然如此\N但是我唸漫畫給她聽時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.12,0:13:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也會露出高興的表情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果買了肉包回來…\N也會很高興的吃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支撐著我的內心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.70,0:14:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經是睡覺的時間了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我不要走嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.94,0:14:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會待妳你身邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一個夢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.48,0:14:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是淡桃色的棉花糖一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.92,0:14:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是最甜美最美妙的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在放入口中的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.93,0:14:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢就像是被施了魔法般\N虛幻的溶化…消逝了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.07,0:14:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後所剩下的\N就是痛苦的回憶…而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精密檢查？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.97,0:14:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是大學的醫院介紹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.21,0:14:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是醫術非常厲害的醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.78,0:14:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要給他們看\N一定會好起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.88,0:14:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭醫生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你不要帶我去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在這之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只有一個請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來這種地方好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.97,0:15:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是去什麼很高級的地方的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.47,0:15:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太緊張\N不就沒有一家人的感覺了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,澤渡真琴小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝妳生日快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.11,0:15:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.28,0:15:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.05,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我決定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.35,0:15:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴到現在為止都沒有什麼生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.45,0:15:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天就是真琴的生日\N對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.79,0:15:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 這樣子也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.50,0:15:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂 真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.36,0:15:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.64,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂\N真琴 很棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 為了紀念生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.45,0:16:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去拍那個吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.69,0:16:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.33,0:16:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴妳在幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來拍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.47,0:16:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 要拍囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要被燙到了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.22,0:16:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴真的很喜歡煙火呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.82,0:16:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀的隆冬中的煙火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.79,0:16:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注視著微微的煙火的\N真琴的側臉也會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.59,0:16:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也會有如仙女棒一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.50,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面臨稍縱即逝的命運吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.11,0:16:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨 名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.48,0:16:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.58,0:17:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔天早上 真琴又發了高燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.19,0:17:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這代表著什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.62,0:17:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有著切身之痛的瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.16,0:17:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在救護車已經要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.63,0:17:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 該準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.07,0:17:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴\N有沒有什麼想做的事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要去哪裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.75,0:17:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要去那個山丘嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.23,0:17:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.43,0:17:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到眺望之丘去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.07,0:17:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴是病人耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.61,0:18:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不早點帶去給醫生看的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.81,0:18:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生是治不好真琴的病的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 秋子阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想要回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回她出生的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生的地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.12,0:18:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眺望之丘嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.23,0:18:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她的夥伴在等著她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.73,0:18:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我以前撿到的狐狸\N轉世而來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.73,0:18:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 你在胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.41,0:18:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.75,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝妳…媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.93,0:19:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.17,0:19:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一以前撿到的小狐狸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.11,0:19:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠很喜歡鈴鐺的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.94,0:19:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子總是在玩\N我錢包上面的鈴鐺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天野…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.63,0:19:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要到那裡去了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到那個山丘…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.20,0:19:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫天野美汐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的名字呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.58,0:19:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.75,0:19:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…琴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.42,0:19:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.65,0:19:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 是個好名字喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天野 謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.36,0:19:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 再一起玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.30,0:20:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 不要睡著了\N就快要到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.04,0:20:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搖看看吧 真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.78,0:20:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳喜歡的鈴鐺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.28,0:20:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓它響看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.65,0:20:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓它多響幾聲看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.25,0:20:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎？\N是妳出生的地方喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一起玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.23,0:20:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了春天…天氣變暖和之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也一定會恢復的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.36,0:20:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 到時候再一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.30,0:20:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 妳怎麼了 真琴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經到眺望之丘了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.48,0:20:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還太早了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.75,0:20:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.12,0:21:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不錯的日子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天野說話還是像個老太婆一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.20,0:21:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請說我言行舉止文雅好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.27,0:21:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回想起一件事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.88,0:21:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.92,0:21:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我初戀情人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經對牠說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.82,0:21:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個叫做澤渡真琴的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.96,0:21:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個多麼溫柔又漂亮的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠仍然記得這一件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.47,0:21:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是\N指引你們兩個人的路標呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.51,0:21:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.21,0:21:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想\N牠們仍然還會在草原上奔跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.05,0:21:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.41,0:22:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那小小的人群中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.08,0:22:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會有新的生命誕生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.22,0:22:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…成長著…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.62,0:22:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,循環不息的生命啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.52,0:22:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見 真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.21,0:22:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從隨風飄流的雲朵之間\N窺視到晴空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.15,0:22:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連熟悉的街道也閃閃發光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.33,0:22:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前奔跑的小小的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.83,0:22:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時的兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.71,0:23:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用天真來蓋過溢出的疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.19,0:23:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間靜悄悄的流動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.19,0:23:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹拂著溫柔的風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.80,0:23:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為凍僵的思念也會化做笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.01,0:23:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼願望都會實現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.28,0:23:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給她的玩偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.78,0:23:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七年前小小的玩偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.69,0:23:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanon第11話\N約定
